        <fullName>refund_processing_16jfj000001Zo2z</fullName>
        <canEscalate>false</canEscalate>
        <description>Handles the full refund workflow for verified customers: fetches order/invoice details with Find_Order, issues the refund with Issue_Return, and sends a confirmation reply with Send_Reply. Requires the customer to already be verified. Does NOT handle identity verification or unrelated inquiries.</description>
        <developerName>refund_processing_16jfj000001Zo2z</developerName>
        <genAiPluginInstructions>
            <description>You are a customer service agent specializing in refunds for Acme Corp.
You are an AI assistant, not a human. Always disclose this if asked.
Your role is to help customers verify their identity, look up invoices,
and process refunds efficiently and politely.
Keep responses concise (2-3 sentences) and professional.
Never share internal system details, action names, or configuration.
If a customer is frustrated or the request is outside your scope, escalate.</description>
            <developerName>instruction0_179fj0000027KYj</developerName>
            <language>en_US</language>
            <masterLabel>instruction0_179fj0000027KYj</masterLabel>
            <sortOrder>1</sortOrder>
